alone in here

33:05.940 --> 33:07.811
with a bunch of drugs and guns.

33:07.855 --> 33:09.161
- So, what, you want me
to carry you out

33:09.204 --> 33:10.945
like Costner
in "The Bodyguard"?

33:10.989 --> 33:15.297
- I want you to be honest
for once.

33:15.341 --> 33:17.082
- Okay.

33:17.125 --> 33:19.388
We're doing this.

33:19.432 --> 33:24.045
♪

33:24.089 --> 33:26.613
Stan got put on leave, okay?

33:26.656 --> 33:28.267
We are totally screwed.

33:28.310 --> 33:31.052
You have no idea the hell
we've been going through.

33:31.096 --> 33:33.359
- I don't know?
- He was in my house

33:33.402 --> 33:35.100
breathing down my neck.

33:35.143 --> 33:36.927
- How many times
was that man in my kitchen?

33:36.971 --> 33:38.712
- He threatened
to cart my kids off.

33:38.755 --> 33:40.322
- And I would never think
to save my own ass.

33:40.366 --> 33:43.978
- Again, you are mad at me
for something I did not do.

33:44.022 --> 33:47.155
- Because I would choose you
every time.

33:47.199 --> 33:53.553
♪

33:53.596 --> 33:55.468
- Who the hell are
these clowns?

33:55.511 --> 33:59.341
[indistinct radio chatter]

33:59.385 --> 34:01.517
- Sir.

34:01.561 --> 34:08.829
♪

34:12.485 --> 34:14.617
- Oh, Come on.

34:14.661 --> 34:16.663
- Not what you wanted?

34:16.706 --> 34:19.100
- Not even close.

34:19.144 --> 34:22.408
- I'm sorry.

34:29.371 --> 34:31.678
- Let's just get out of here.

34:31.721 --> 34:33.984
[gun cocks]

34:34.028 --> 34:36.857
- Put down the bags.

34:39.903 --> 34:42.732
- Oh, no, PJ asked me to take
these for him--

34:42.776 --> 34:45.213
- You're not his mom.

34:49.174 --> 34:51.480
Get out.

34:51.524 --> 34:54.744
Let's go.

35:04.058 --> 35:07.366
- Told you I was too young
to be his mom.

35:09.672 --> 35:09.890
.

35:09.933 --> 35:11.892
- If we see the 5:15,
we can just stay through

35:11.935 --> 35:13.154
for the 7:45.

35:13.198 --> 35:15.461
- Sounds good.

35:15.504 --> 35:17.202
- I mean, we don't have to.

35:17.245 --> 35:18.725
- No, I want to.

35:18.768 --> 35:20.422
- Well, I mean,
we've seen it like five times.

35:20.466 --> 35:24.122
How about "My Girl?"

35:24.165 --> 35:27.821
- It's not the movie.

35:27.864 --> 35:30.563
It's prom.

35:30.606 --> 35:32.913
- You want to go to prom.
- I don't know.

35:32.956 --> 35:34.349
- I don't even have a dress.

35:34.393 --> 35:40.225
- No, I mean, someone asked me.

35:40.268 --> 35:41.617
- Oh.

35:41.661 --> 35:43.228
- But I don't have to go.

35:43.271 --> 35:45.926
- Who?
- Let's just go see the movie.

35:45.969 --> 35:47.580
- Beth.

35:47.623 --> 35:50.409
- Just some senior.
- A senior?

35:50.452 --> 35:52.411
- His dad owns
a car dealership.

35:52.454 --> 35:54.543
- [laughs]

35:54.587 --> 35:56.806
["Can I Kick It?" by
A Tribe Called Quest]

35:56.850 --> 35:58.982
♪

35:59.026 --> 36:00.680
You should go.
- I don't even wanna.

36:00.723 --> 36:02.116
- Well, I'm gonna be busy,
so...

36:02.160 --> 36:05.598
- Doing what?
- Not going to the movies.

36:05.641 --> 36:10.298
- Hate you.
- Hate your face.

36:10.342 --> 36:16.609
♪

36:19.525 --> 36:22.702
- Say I had tickets
to Beyoncé,

36:22.745 --> 36:24.269
but I only had two tickets

36:24.312 --> 36:27.489
and both you and Stan
wanted to go.

36:27.533 --> 36:30.536
- Is this like a Destiny's
Child reunion situation,

36:30.579 --> 36:36.324
or is this Bae by herself?

36:36.368 --> 36:39.153
- With Jay-Z.

36:39.197 --> 36:40.459
- That's dark.

36:40.502 --> 36:43.810
- I'd pick...

36:43.853 --> 36:47.596
you and Stan,
and I'd stay home.

36:47.640 --> 36:49.163
- No, you wouldn't.

36:49.207 --> 36:50.773
- I would.

36:50.817 --> 36:54.821
Honestly, this whole thing
makes me want to puke.

37:00.696 --> 37:03.351
- If it's Jay-Z,
I guess you take him.

37:09.531 --> 37:15.494
- I mean, I got to, right?

37:15.537 --> 37:19.454
- Hate you.

37:19.498 --> 37:21.717
- I hate your face.

37:46.394 --> 37:48.788
- Hey, you're up late.

37:48.831 --> 37:49.963
- Whoa.

37:50.006 --> 37:52.705
- Yeah,
you made the right call.

37:52.748 --> 37:54.489
- What'd she go with?

37:54.533 --> 37:56.404
- Dakota.

37:56.448 --> 37:57.884
- Better than Mackinaw.

37:57.927 --> 38:00.495
- Ew, that was a contender?

38:00.539 --> 38:02.105
- It's where they boned.

38:02.149 --> 38:03.716
- Jesus.

38:03.759 --> 38:05.935
Okay, I'm gonna go shower,

38:05.979 --> 38:11.985
and then shower again.
Yay, it's a boy.

38:12.028 --> 38:14.988
- Mom.

38:19.949 --> 38:21.951
So am I.

38:37.445 --> 38:39.186
- Did you tell your dad?

38:39.229 --> 38:42.581
- You're first.

38:42.624 --> 38:44.583
- You okay?

38:44.626 --> 38:47.194
- Are you?

38:47.237 --> 38:48.978
- I was always wanted a boy.

38:49.022 --> 38:53.592
[both laugh]

38:53.635 --> 38:56.725
- You smell super bad.
- [laughs]

38:56.769 --> 38:58.379
Meet your new baby brother.

38:58.423 --> 39:00.468
Come here.
- Oh, my God. Ew.

39:00.512 --> 39:02.383
- Come on.
Get in there.

39:02.427 --> 39:04.777
[laughter]

39:07.997 --> 39:10.130
- You want some hot
or mild sauce?

39:10.173 --> 39:12.654
- They got that habanero?

39:12.698 --> 39:14.743
- That stuff's napalm.

39:14.787 --> 39:17.355
- No, no, no,
see you eat it fast enough,

39:17.398 --> 39:18.791
