with the sister?

39:31.804 --> 39:34.459
- I'm out of the friend zone.

39:34.502 --> 39:36.374
- Already?
- Yeah, man.

39:36.417 --> 39:38.550
You can't turn this down.
- Dude.

39:38.593 --> 39:40.595
Dude.
[both laugh]

39:40.639 --> 39:42.771
- Let me run with it
for a while.

39:42.815 --> 39:44.469
- All right.
- We'll see what turns up.

39:44.512 --> 39:45.731
- Yeah, yeah.

39:45.774 --> 39:49.169
- Hook me up with another
spice bomb.

39:49.212 --> 39:52.781
- You're an animal.
- [laughs]

